<topic id="ofbENT-set_up_basic_auth">
  <title>How to Set up Basic Authentication</title>
  <body>
    <p>By default, <term>Basic Authentication</term> support is disabled. To enable it, set the
      following property in the <filepath>config/feedback-application.properties</filepath>
      file:<codeblock outputclass="language-bourne">feedback.basic.authentication.enabled=true</codeblock></p>
    <note><term>Basic Authentication</term> works only with credentials associated with local (DB)
      accounts (not with LDAP or OAuth accounts).</note>
  </body>
